snippet.title: Skulls of the Shogun: Bone-a-Fide Edition coming to PlayStation 4
snippet.description:
Skulls of the Shogun: Bone-a-Fide Edition, a fast-paced turn-based action-strategy game, is coming to PlayStation 4 with a heaping helping of crunchy content! 

For more details and sweet Skulls gear, check out http://www.skullsoftheshogun.com
